uploadJsonDocument.display-name: Upload document metadata (JSON) or document file

uploadPdfDocument.display-name: Upload document metadata (JSON) or document file

__package__.yml.rawContents:
types:
  UploadDocumentResponse:
    discriminated: false
    union:
      - DocumentMetadata
      - DocumentUploadResult
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  DocumentMetadata:
    properties:
      id: optional<integer>
      title: optional<string>
      author: optional<string>
      tags: optional<list<unknown>>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  DocumentUploadResult:
    properties:
      fileId: optional<string>
      status: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    uploadJsonDocument:
      path: /documents/upload
      method: POST
      auth: true
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Upload document metadata (JSON) or document file
      request:
        name: UploadDocumentRequest
        body:
          properties:
            title: optional<string>
            author: optional<string>
            tags: optional<list<string>>
        content-type: application/json
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: UploadDocumentResponse
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - request: {}
          response:
            body:
              id: 1
              title: title
              author: author
              tags:
                - key: value
    uploadPdfDocument:
      path: /documents/upload
      method: POST
      auth: true
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: Upload document metadata (JSON) or document file
      request:
        body: bytes
        content-type: application/pdf
      response:
        docs: Successful response
        type: UploadDocumentResponse
        status-code: 200
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml

    scheme: bearer
auth: BearerAuthScheme
